high_descs: move to the corner of the kitchen where the microwave is
grab the knife off the counter to the left of the microwave
walk over to the fridge
place the knife inside the pan in the fridge
take out the pan from the microwave
bring the pan over to the sink
place the pan down on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a knife in it to the right of the sink

high_descs: Take a step ahead towards the kitchen counter with the microwave on it.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the knife handle down inside the metal pan that is in the fridge.
Remove the pan with the knife in it, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the metal pan with the knife in it onto the counter in the corner behind and to the right of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a metal pan with a large metal knife in it onto the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Look forward at counter with two bottles
Pick up knife with yellow handle to left of bottles
Go to refrigerator on the right
Open refrigerator door, place knife in square copper pot
Pick up square copper pot out of refrigerator
Turn left, walk to sink
Place pot on far, right corner of counter, to right of sink
anns.task_desc: Place knife in pot in refrigerator, place pot on counter
